    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1951-12-11T18:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1951-12-11T18:00:00-05:00" n="134"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d134">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">320/12–1251: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The United States Representative at the United Nations</hi>
                        (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Austin</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                        <lb/>
                        <gloss target="#t_niact1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">niact</hi>
                        </gloss>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1951-12-12T00:00:00+01:00"
                            >December 12, 1951—midnight.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <gloss target="#t_Delga1">Delga</gloss> 638. Re contributions. In light action
                    Comte Five does <gloss target="#t_Dept1">Dept</gloss> wish <gloss
                        target="#t_USGADel1">USGADel</gloss> staff urge Canada reintroduce proposal
                    plenary next week. If proposal to have any chance success it wld in judgment
                        <gloss target="#t_USGADel1">USGADel</gloss> staff require direct approach
                    foreign mins or heads of govts Commonwealth, Western Europe and Latin America to
                    change abstentions to affirmative votes. <gloss target="#t_USGADel1"
                        >USGADel</gloss> staff opinion is such action valuable assure US reduction
                    1953 financial year to 33⅓ percent, to improve presentation to Congress and stop
                    present trend so-called underdeveloped states voting irresponsibly on budget and
                    financial proposals <gloss target="#t_UN1">UN</gloss>.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Austin</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
